    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105430/extras/991243afae7ec02312da39cd843bd5e7.avif?t=1750943419\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105430/extras_big/991243afae7ec02312da39cd843bd5e7.avif?t=1750943419 width=800 height=258 /></span>Steven is a retro-style survival frenzy starring a furious swan on the run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After breaking free from the iron grip of a tyrant king, <strong>Steven</strong>—a lone, long-necked rebel—must fight his way through endless waves of knights hellbent on ending his flight. In this <strong>vampire-survivor-inspired</strong> arena game, you’ll glide, peck, and devour your enemies, growing stronger with every second you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield bizarre upgrades like <i>Faster Speed</i>, <i>Neck Extension</i>, <i>Egg Hunts</i>, and more, turning Steven from a graceful bird into a ridiculous powerhouse. Hatch loyal swanlings to join the fray, extend your deadly neck to slap down foes, and keep the chaos going as the screen floods with enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105430/extras/d0d3bc86eeb6b52524e0bedefd0b3907.poster.avif?t=1750943419\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105430/extras/d0d3bc86eeb6b52524e0bedefd0b3907.webm?t=1750943419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105430/extras/d0d3bc86eeb6b52524e0bedefd0b3907.mp4?t=1750943419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless action with rogue-lite progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A growing arsenal of weird and wonderful swan powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Helpers hatched from eggs (because why not?)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls, deep chaos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive longer to unlock even wilder upgrades</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Visual Style:</strong> Crafted in a <strong>3-color palette inspired by classic Game Boy games</strong>, <i>Steven</i> blends nostalgic pixel art with smooth modern gameplay for a perfect mix of old-school charm and new-school mayhem.</p>",
